description:
New Scuderia Ferrari signing Charles Leclerc put in a solid 157 laps during his first run in the SF90 on the second day of pre-season testing, and claimed the fastest time of the day as well! Jump on board with the Monegasque for a his first lap in anger as a Ferrari man.

title: Charles Leclerc Goes Fastest for Ferrari on Day 2 | F1 Testing 2019

description: Ferrari has talked of trying to be "extreme" with its 2019 F1 car, but from the images seen so far it doesn't appear to be an overly complex design. Jake Boxall-Legge joins Glenn Freeman to highlight the areas where it's clear Ferrari has made big changes, and to discuss if the more simple parts of the car are a launch specification, or Ferrari sticking to its guns with concepts it has faith in
title: How Ferrari has mixed 'extreme' with simple: 2019 SF90 F1 technical analysis

title: Discovering the SF90

description: E' stata presentata a Maranello la nuova Ferrari SF90, la nuova monoposto di Vettel e Leclerc che correrà nella stagione F1 2019. Una vettura che evolve i concetti vincenti visti nel 2018 introducendo una nuova verniciatura opaca che innova il look della Rossa. Scopriamo come è fatta nell'approfondimento di Paolo Ciccarone, Diletta Colombo ed Emiliano Perucca Orfei
title: Ferrari SF90 | Ecco la nuova F1 2019

description: Every Formula 1 team set its fastest time of pre-season on the penultimate day of the final test, with Ferrari making a bold statement out front. But Charles Leclerc's best lap was far from the full potential of the SF90, which looks superb on track. Ben Anderson is joined by Edd Straw and Jack Cozens in Barcelona to discuss what the fastest day of 2019 testing told us, how the midfield battle is shaping up, and where Mercedes fits into all of this as it avoided setting a headline lap time.
title: 'Ferrari can go even quicker' - F1 testing's fastest day yet
